    <title>使用next主题踩到的坑</title>
    <url>/2020/10/28/err-NexT/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>文章内容仅供参考，踩坑不负责，下载next主题的时间：2020-10-23（在此之前GitHub上的最近更新时间是9-2）</p>
<a id="more"></a>

<h1 id="下载链接错误"><a href="#下载链接错误" class="headerlink" title="下载链接错误"></a>下载链接错误</h1><p>通过别人的博客知道hexo支持一个非常好看的next主题，我当然不会错过。Google之后发现NexT官方文档居然是全中文的，这下可把我乐坏了，美滋滋！然而事情没这么简单，<strong>以下为官方文档原话</strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p>Hexo 安装主题的方式非常简单，只需要将主题文件拷贝至站点目录的 <code>themes</code> 目录下， 然后修改下配置文件即可。具体到 NexT 来说，安装步骤如下。</p>
<p>$ cd your-hexo-site<br>$ git clone <a href="https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next">https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next</a> themes/next</p>
</blockquote>
<p>看到这个路径在github上，出于习惯我点进去看了一眼。不得了，最近一次更新还是在去年初，readme上一个迁移提示，大意是说这个仓库不更新了，想用新版本需要去新的仓库（链接：<a href="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next">NexT v6 and v7 </a>）。所以说，<strong>如果需要下载最新版本的NexT主题的命令应该是</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight awk"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https:<span class="regexp">//gi</span>thub.com<span class="regexp">/theme-next/</span>hexo-theme-<span class="keyword">next</span> themes/<span class="keyword">next</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>到这里我就留了个心眼，要时刻注意不被这个官方文档坑</p>
<h1 id="设置语言为中文"><a href="#设置语言为中文" class="headerlink" title="设置语言为中文"></a>设置语言为中文</h1><p><strong>在NexT的官方文档中是这样说的：</strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p>编辑 <strong>站点配置文件</strong>， 将 <code>language</code> 设置成你所需要的语言。建议明确设置你所需要的语言，例如选用简体中文，配置如下：</p>
<p>language: zh-Hans</p>
</blockquote>
<img src="/2020/10/28/err-NexT/image-20201028132326518.png" class>

<p>然而实际上新版本中zh-Hans已经改为了zh-CN</p>
<img src="/2020/10/28/err-NexT/image-20201028132159541.png" class>

<p><strong>所以使用简体中文应该设置：</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight avrasm"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="symbol">language:</span> <span class="built_in">zh</span>-CN</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h1 id="侧边社交栏链接"><a href="#侧边社交栏链接" class="headerlink" title="侧边社交栏链接"></a>侧边社交栏链接</h1><p><strong>官方文档如下：</strong></p>
<img src="/2020/10/28/err-NexT/image-20201028165632286.png" class>

<p>实际在使用中应该这样</p>
<figure class="highlight less"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">social</span>:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">GitHub</span>: <span class="attribute">https</span>:<span class="comment">//github.com/Gypsophila123 || fab fa-github</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">G-Mail</span>: yuanjie15115580021<span class="variable">@gmail</span>.com || fa fa-envelope</span><br><span class="line">  #<span class="attribute">Weibo</span>: <span class="attribute">https</span>:<span class="comment">//weibo.com/yourname || fab fa-weibo</span></span><br><span class="line">  #<span class="attribute">Google</span>: <span class="attribute">https</span>:<span class="comment">//plus.google.com/yourname || fab fa-google</span></span><br><span class="line">  #<span class="attribute">Twitter</span>: <span class="attribute">https</span>:<span class="comment">//twitter.com/yourname || fab fa-twitter</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="number">#FB</span> <span class="attribute">Page</span>: <span class="attribute">https</span>:<span class="comment">//www.facebook.com/yourname || fab fa-facebook</span></span><br><span class="line">  #<span class="attribute">StackOverflow</span>: <span class="attribute">https</span>:<span class="comment">//stackoverflow.com/yourname || fab fa-stack-overflow</span></span><br><span class="line">  #<span class="attribute">YouTube</span>: <span class="attribute">https</span>:<span class="comment">//youtube.com/yourname || fab fa-youtube</span></span><br><span class="line">  #<span class="attribute">Instagram</span>: <span class="attribute">https</span>:<span class="comment">//instagram.com/yourname || fab fa-instagram</span></span><br><span class="line">  #<span class="attribute">Skype</span>: <span class="attribute">skype</span>:yourname?call|chat || fab fa-skype</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">social_icons</span>:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">enable</span>: true # 是否显示图标</span><br><span class="line">  # Icon Mappings</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">GitHub</span>: github</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">icons_only</span>: false # 仅显示图标</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">transition</span>: false</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<img src="/2020/10/28/err-NexT/image-20201028165537958.png" class>]]></content>
